   _1.2325 Canadian dollars, up from 1.2315
   The British pound edged up to $1.8707 from $1.8645.
   London bullion dealers fixed a recommended gold price of $444.30
a troy ounce, down from $449.25 last Friday. London bullion markets
were closed Monday for a national holiday.
