<1ST_LINE>u n AM-RifleProbe 1stLd-Writethru a0832 05-03 0513</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>AM-Rifle Probe, 1st Ld-Writethru, a0832,500</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>Eds: Subs 4th graf pvs, bgng, ``Within a ...'' with 2 grafs to add
Colt official's comment; INSERTS 1 graf after graf 8 pvs, bgng,
``Nelson said... with alleged Indonesia sale, pick up graf 9 pvs,
